<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>test someone for something • test someone on something</xh5><p> <i>test someone for something—</i>perform a medical check on a person to detect a possible disease, etc.: The doctors <u>tested him for</u> malaria and other illnesses.</p><p><i>test someone on something—</i>ask questions to find out how much a person knows about a subject: The teacher <u>tested me on</u> my knowledge of French.</p> </entry>
